title: Lombardi's Week 5 Watch List and Last-Second Fantasy Advice | GM Street (Ep. 316)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier link up to discuss the Colts' loss to the Patriots (02:00) before highlighting their favorite matchups coming up this weekend (16:45). Then Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly of 'The Dantasy Football Podcast' distribute some fantasy football advice (47:15).
